Italy’s Consob Extends Short-Sales Ban to Nov. 11

-- B y   M a r c o   B e r t a c c h e
-- 
2011-09-28T17:31:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/italy-s-consob-extends-short-sales-ban-to-nov-11.html
Italy’s market regulator extended a
ban on short-selling of financial stocks, it said on its website
today.  The ban, due to expire on Sept. 30, will remain in place
until Nov. 11.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Bertacche at 
 mbertacche@bloomberg.net  